node.text: Ah, evening spritzes, negronis, and your amazing puttanesca pizza!

We miss doing the simple things,  like the table setting, plating our food, serving clients at their table,  noisy dinner parties, the sounds of joy and laughter, having our little team of seven all together again, parties, celebrations. What do you miss most? 
Stay safe. Stay sane. Stay home. We miss you. 
#casamanini #cucinaitaliana #italia in #serangoongardens #andràtuttobene #circuitbreakersg #covid19 #thenewnormal #weloveourguests
😥💗😘miss our gatherings with u running around the background ...
Can’t wait to be able to dine in again soon (hopefully!) 🙏🏻
@jasnaure seafood risotto and the other - an open ravioli with morel mushrooms and river vegetables. That was a  wry special dish as Nonna Manini sent the model mushrooms to us. 😁
What’s the seafood one and the morel mushroom one was if?
Ah, evening spritzes, negronis, and your amazing puttanesca pizza!
